Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.88,0:00:07.98,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(50,270)\fad(600,600)}回\N锅\N肉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.31,0:00:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了  不过我也只能做出这种东西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.46,0:00:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好厉害  这不是回锅肉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正好肚子饿扁了  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.94,0:00:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在里面放了一点东西提味  不知你能不能吃出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提味啊  你还真是够认真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  应该说是只有豆酱的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是该说提味凸显得太深了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  倒不如说这个味道越嚼越难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的是背道而驰！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:26.97,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N23
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是相当不错…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪  美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:44.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}纸上：河童  很帅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是何方妖孽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童？  为什么现在要画河童
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她还说「很帅吧」…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她这次画的画虽然幻想色彩很强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定某种意义上还算有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:04.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这里的巨人指宫崎骏著名电影「幽灵公主」里出场的山神麒麟兽\N原型是日本传说中的巨人「ダイダラボッチ」，传说其一晚上就造出了富士山和琵琶湖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「巨人+河童」之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童  嘿  可以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童  河童啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:15.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}河童的发音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KAPPA  KAPPA  PA  PA…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}寄生虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PARASITE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就顺着这样开始玩「绘画接龙」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PARASITE？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PARASITE是这种生物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然画了这个箭头  就是说她在邀请我玩「绘画接龙」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就勉为其难玩一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是PARASITE呢  TE  TE…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}纸上天狗说的话：时间不够了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:55.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}上文祐子把寄生虫的日文发音PARASAITO读成了PARASHITE。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且天狗什么的…  她把PARASITE的TO读成TE了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:03:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  算了  是天狗呢  天狗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GU  GU  GU…  GU！  骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}天狗的日文发音是TENGU，祐子写成了TENGO。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是TENGO！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TENGO是什么玩意啊  TENGO！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  是故意写错的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生可不会犯这种幼稚的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她在图上画了天狗  还特地写了文字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂她的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然总觉得无法理解  这里只能附和她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用GO来接了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}GOKUU-悟空，画上右下角的字：你给我画小一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个倦怠的悟空是怎么回事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  啊咧  悟空？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(390,360)\fs18}GOKUU
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我画的应该是天狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,360)\fs18}TENGU
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  心里想着「GU」却写成了「GO」我能够理解啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下回头得让她请客饮料了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  接下来  是U呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U  U…  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:09.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}纸上：我没法画得很好！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海胆  不对  是兔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,360)\fs18}UNI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,360)\fs18}USA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是牛吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,360)\fs18}USI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个牛也画得太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舌头  是舌头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,360)\fs18}SHITA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就是TA了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TA  TA  计程车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(395,360)\fs18}TAKUSHII
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什…什么鬼东西啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是TAXI而是TAXY啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  随便画个东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:48.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}美绪把寿司（SUSI）倒过来写成SI-SU-。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  连业界用语都用上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就好画了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}超人的日语发音「SUUPAAMAN」的结尾为N，无法再接。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  这样不就输了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这里  这样做的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:03.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}祐子在后面加了个假名ZU，成为SUPERMANS。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:18.85,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,340)\fad(600,600)}围\N棋\N足\N球\N部\N3
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好闲啊  关口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  关口  来玩「异口同声」一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我先开始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异口同…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关口  反正你闲着  偶尔也陪我玩一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  关口…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:06.60,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N24
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:15.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}依旧是5-7-5的俳句格式\N最上川是在山形县的一条河，这里只是为了凑俳句的格式而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘写作业  罚站在走廊的  最上川  by祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是忘记写作业了  就被罚站在走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间  要怎样度过  最上川  by祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大家  有鹿  有只鹿…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么校长要把鹿…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校…校长  鹿…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大家  校长他…濒死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  鹿煎饼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  大家  校长要死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬上去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞起来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那样摔下来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.75,0:08:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又爬上去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬下来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束手无策了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  DEATH  校长…  DEATH  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大家  听我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…  校…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走廊上一切正常！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是从心底发出的最真挚的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是因为想包庇校长  或者说是嫌说明麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许只是为了对刚才演出了那场死斗的勇者们致以敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅雨  过早汇入  最上川  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵…  意义不明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:09.35,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,300)\fad(600,600)}10\N円\N足\N球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那么  美绪来当裁判哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10円足球不是不需要裁判吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧啧啧  你不懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是心情的问题  心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  开球吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样都行  攻过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后出布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱出哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲨…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}鲨鱼「サメ」和韩语的我爱你开头的发音都是「SA」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:34.67,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N25
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抓到了一只蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎…慎重地  总之要慎重地行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让这只恶心的恶之根源再次在这个家中滋生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计策…必须想出最优计策
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  杀虫剂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是无法一击杀虫  就会有让它逃走的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且更重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看到它扭曲挣扎的样子！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  洗涤剂怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在矮脚桌的周围洒上洗涤剂用于封住它的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再万无一失地伺机捉住它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  会…会飞！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是逃走的话这家伙一定会飞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦飞起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会胡乱地突然飞过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是飞到我身上…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  要是飞向我的脸！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  等…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要是飞到嘴里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是飞到嘴里的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次就给我来一发ROCK'N'ROLL！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是棒极了  没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿起这个碗的一瞬间的选项只有「死」和「死掉」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DEATH  or  DIE！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能…只能那样做了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  阪…阪本先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请救救我  这…这个里面有蟑…  蟑…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是蟑螂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊  想要我捉住的话  就把碗打开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我就说把碗举起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话怎么捉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.49,0:15:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你在说什么啊  居然要我解除这恶之根源的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是潘多拉之盒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开以后灾祸就会降临啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  不把碗打开的话怎么抓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请自己打开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么打得开啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的点心是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得正是时候！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士一点都不怕虫  一定可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  能不能帮我处理一下这个碗里的蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R  R  R  ROCK'N'ROLL！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思  那么就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:16:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么看我一发解决它哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明…我明明是如此认真地烦恼着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人却…  这个人却…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我最讨厌博士了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.63,0:16:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我是骗你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能会讨厌博士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.13,0:16:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  我最喜欢你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  真拿博士没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:17:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  ROCK'N'ROLL开始了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:09.10,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,300)\fad(400,400)}数\N到\N10\N的\N话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我热死了  可以出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  不是刚刚才进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  数到10就出去怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20㏒√10
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我数到10了  可以出去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「1…2」不这样数的话不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:41.95,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,350)\fad(600,600)}围\N棋\N足\N球\N部\N4
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  大家都说要去补习班  就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有关口一个人  好无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧  话说关口你不是说要去补习班来着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:13.18,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N26
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  咖喱怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  马上就好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经超级饿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  你那里怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有钓到大鱼的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是盛宴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  已经差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了  超美味超级咖喱完成之卷！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边还要煮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做咖喱之前准备好的话就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:07.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}日本俗语「赤子泣くとも蓋取るな」，意为饭煮到一半不准揭盖。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  毕竟说是「即使小孩哭也不准揭盖」  啊哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  要是带蛋黄酱来就好了  果然吃咖喱就是要放蛋黄酱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋黄…蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  你吃咖喱放什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我呕～  开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  不是的  这不是你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  你看  我这里还有凉粉可以吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉粉…开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.69,0:19:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:52.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}恶搞北斗神拳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙的血是什么颜色的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭的咖喱和米饭都完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉粉的话还有一份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RELEASE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这里还剩下一盒凉粉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一盒吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我想让大家轮流着吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这次是我和美绪不对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以麻衣你先请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别给我一口全部吃掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你多虑了  我又不是魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我先开动喽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呛到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.82,0:21:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  来玩牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不玩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:21:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话  露营会以遗憾收场的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:22:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的最后来玩牌  用HAPPY  END来画上句点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.67,0:22:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人在这种时候不是要喝酒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.76,0:22:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  麻衣你会不会那样想？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.06,0:22:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也带来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.04,0:22:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道  美绪你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.76,0:22:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿嘿  就是那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏了  这样就坏了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.36,0:22:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.78,0:22:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管了！  我要喝啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.49,0:22:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪  快停下  会死的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.99,0:22:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣你还有多的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是苹果酒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.68,0:23:09.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}原作中出现的安慰祐子的狗狗巴蒂。
