Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:17.16,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}まさか　いや　片思い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:16.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an4}両\N思\Nい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:19.53,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やばい！　視線会合っちゃた！！！
