Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:14.31,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}和你生硬的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:13.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}两\N个\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:17.16,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}难道  不对  是单相思
